title: Topaz  Restyle 1.0.0 [Serial]
description:
Topaz  Restyle 1.0.0

Topaz Restyle lets you explore new artistic and creative possibilities for your images and helps you 

achieve looks you might not have thought of otherwise. Transform your images with just one click using 

over a thousand easily searchable styles and looks. ReStyle offers inspiration through exploring the 

unending possibilities included in this product, and as a result, you can quickly achieve your vision 

or even extend and enhance the original vision for your image.

-Latest technology mapping. In ReStyle put forward the process of displaying color and tone. The new 

technology allows high quality convert images to different styles.
-New Styles / Methods for creating styles. ReStyle create presets using the color and tone of the 

original image, allowing you to save your own unique styles for future use.
-Blending modes. In ReStyle included various settings blending modes on the merits of 8 different 

types for each style.
-HSL technology is a 5-color sliders style. Using a unique control hue, saturation and brightness.
-Masking. The module is attached to the mask, and each tab contains a complete set of different tools.
-Design of the user interface. ReStyle to continue the development of more modern and efficient 

interface to improve usability, workflow, and overall aesthetics.
